\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
命题3.1.2 (夹逼原理)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

的一个空心领域内有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{1}(x)\le f(x)\le f_{2}(x).
\]

\end_inset

若
\begin_inset Formula $f_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{2}$
\end_inset

在
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

处的极限存在且等于
