\begin_layout Paragraph
定理3.1.7 (单调有界原理)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

定义在
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0})$
\end_inset

上, 若
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

单调上升有上界, 或
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

单调下降有下界, 则
